ComicInfo.Summary: Penny and Ace arrive on Urth, a decoy world with time-space coordinate "forwarding", to save Gina from the apocalyptic nightmares who are out to destroy what they believe to be Earth! Only the dimensional plague-swarm known as the Orzz are on to the ploy and attempt to hijack the rescue ship... after an obligatory blood-feast!
